ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectThe Mohawks of Akwesasne Tsikaristisere/Dundee Claim Settlement ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to ENTER INTO and EXECUTE, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the MOHAWKS OF AKWESASNE TSIKARISTISERE/DUNDEE CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Mohawks of Akwesasne, a summary of which is set out in the Schedule A.
